snippet.title: Birb Café Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
After a much requested rework, we're proud to announce Birb Café launches May 12!

Make sure to check out the updated demo, cute birb awaits! And if you really like it, wishlist so you can enjoy it when it drops!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1579300/
https://birbgames.itch.io/birb-cafe
